<br>
  I was on a raid in HHK last weekend, and a bard feared me.  This is strange, as I am a player on Vallon Zek...bard fearing was supposedly nerfed to where you can't target Player Characters.  We were alone, on the steep cliffs of East Karana.<br>
  <br>
  Is it possible that the bard targeted herself, and while I was in range of the area of effect, it worked on me, but not her?  Or...was bard fearing never really nerfed at all.<br>
  <br>
  There was some lvl discrepancy, as she got it and a snare to stick while i have 96 MR...so it definitely freaked me out a little when it happend.  I activated my lev ring and booked out of there off the ledge to regroup, and get another poison ready.  Never saw her again.<br>
<br>
Thoughts?<br>
<br>
-Venomss <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulirintz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lirin TZ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/10/01 11:57:53 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/ribbon_small.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bards</span><hr size=1> yeah, bards can fear on the PvP servers.  the trick is to not have the person you want feared targeted when you sing it.   <p><a href=http://eq.castersrealm.com/players/view_profile.asp?Id=86678>Liringlas Lookinglass</a><br>
Bard of the 51st Song<br>Fennin Ro
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=cylant>Cylant</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/10/01 2:14:48 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bards</span><hr size=1> The reason this happens is that when verant first removed fear, they didn't bother to code in prevention for ae fear.  Any type of area effect fear works on the pvp servers, you just have to cast it on yourself. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulammfallaway.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lamm Fallaway</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/11/01 9:03:12 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> re</span><hr size=1> ---------------<br>
you just have to cast it on yourself. <br>
--------------------------<br>
<br>
